onateur et contribuez ainsi au \ufb01nancement des travaux de la reconstruction.", "short_description": "Orange pr\u00e9sente \u00ab Eternelle Notre-Dame \u00bb, la premi\u00e8re exp\u00e9dition immersive en r\u00e9alit\u00e9 virtuelle \u00e0 Notre-Dame de Paris.\n\nPlongez dans l\u2019histoire de la cath\u00e9drale gr\u00e2ce \u00e0 la r\u00e9alit\u00e9 virtuelle, d\u00e9couvrez des endroits inaccessibles et entrez dans l\u2019Histoire\u2026.\n\nGr\u00e2ce \u00e0 votre casque, vous pourrez explorer Notre-Dame de Paris \u00e0 travers les si\u00e8cles, totalement recr\u00e9\u00e9e num\u00e9riquement."}]}, "developer_name": "Emissive", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.orange.com/en/eternal-notre-dame/privacy-notice", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://www.orange.com/en/eternal-notre-dame/application-general-terms-and-conditions-use", "publisher_name": "Orange SA", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.orange.com/en/eternal-notre-dame", "category": "ENTERTAINMENT", "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2837265163266059", "context_category": "ENTERTAINMENT"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "726368587961803"}, {"id": "661880351198839"}, {"id": "439804597133915"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["DOCUMENTARY_HISTORY", "EDUCATIONAL", "EXPERIENCE_360_NON_GAME"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED_FOR_DOWNLOAD", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["fr", "es", "en_GB", "zh_HK", "zh_TW"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "8229864767038000"}, "review_messages": [""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974459_1266365834135040_7668236052259120550_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360